Latex Units and Lengths:
# https://www.overleaf.com/learn/latex/Lengths_in_LaTeX

pt                          # point
mm                          # millimeter
cm                          # centimeter
in                          # inch
ex                          # heigh of lowercase x in current font
em                          # width of uppercase M in current font
mu                          # 1/18 em
sp                          # special low-level point. 65536sp=1pt

\setlength{\name}{val}      #
\baselineskip               # vertical distance between lines in paragraph
\columnsep                  # distance between columns
\columnwidth                #
\evensidemargin             #
\linewidth                  #
\oddsidemargin              #
\paperwidth                 #
\paperheight                #
\parindent                  #
\parskip                    # vertical space between paragraphs
\tabcolsep                  # column space in tables
\textheight                 # of the page
\textwidth                  # of the page
\topmargin                  #
